Description: Functions for accessing, subsetting, and comparing genomic datasets to identify Rapidly-evolving Exons (REEs). Includes an assortment of convenience functions for pattern matching and wrapper functions for to calculate stats when performing multiple sequence alignment for up to thousands of loci.
